  <para><emphasis>Drop on Node by Indexpath</emphasis></para>
  <para>
    <itemizedlist>
      <listitem>
        <para>
          This action drops a dragged item onto the node you specify.
        </para>
      </listitem>
      <listitem>
        <para>
          You give the path to the node you want to drop the item onto using an indexpath.
        </para>
      </listitem>
      <listitem>
        <para>
          This is achieved by:
          
          <itemizedlist>
            <listitem>
              <para>
                Moving the cursor over the node.
              </para>
            </listitem>
            <listitem>
              <para>
                If the tree is not expanded, it is expanded.
              </para>
            </listitem>
            <listitem>
              <para>
                Letting loose the mouse button you specify.
              </para>
            </listitem>
          </itemizedlist>
        </para>
      </listitem>
      <listitem>
        <para>
          Precede this action with a <emphasis>drag</emphasis> action.
        </para>
      </listitem>
      <listitem>
        <para>
          Parameters:
          
          <itemizedlist>
            <listitem>
              <para>
